These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, subway, car, helicopter
House: art-deco, colonial, wooden, craftsman
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, chef, freelancer, software-developer
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, backgammon, billiard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, jazz, rock
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, mouse, rabbit
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, ivory, emerald, chestnut
 1. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing snooker is the colonial house##1
 3. the craftsman house is the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is the colonial house##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is between the person who likes red and the freelancer##2
 6. the teacher is on the right of the software-developer##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
12. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
13. the wooden house is on the left of the fan of rock##1
14. the craftsman house is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
16. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
17. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
18. the owner of the rabbit is the person who likes chestnut##1
19. the fan of folk is the art-deco house##1
20. the fan of jazz is on the left of the chef##1
21. the person playing snooker is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Transport      | helicopter        | car   | skateboard         | subway  |
| House          | wooden         | colonial   | art-deco   | craftsman |
| Job         | freelancer | chef    | software-developer | teacher   |
| Game   | mah-jongg        | snooker  | billiard      | backgammon   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | rock       | folk        | ambient   |
| Pet           | rabbit        | mouse      | goldfish    | lizard    |
| Color         | chestnut | emerald | red      | ivory   |

