There 4 different types of food: banana, papaya, plum, pumpkin
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, orange, blood-red, light-blue
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, daffodil, amaryllis, balloon-flower
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, reading, dancing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, december, april, may
City: rome, liverpool, colone, hannover
 1. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 3. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 5. the person eating banana is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
10. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to rome is the person who growsamaryllis##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
15. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
17. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
18. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person traveling to hannover##1
19. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
20. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4
21. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta         | coffee     | tea        | mirinda  |
| Food          | plum          | banana     | pumpkin    | papaya   |
| Color   | green          | blood-red      | orange      | light-blue   |
| Flower   | daisy     | balloon-flower  | daffodil      | amaryllis  |
| Hobby           | cooking         | dancing     | collecting     | reading   |
| Birthday         | april | may | december | march |
