 9. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
10. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
12. the person playing poker is the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
14. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the fan of soul##1
15. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
16. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
17. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's sport is basketball##1
18. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
