 8. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 9. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
13. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
14. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
15. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who likes yellow and the alhambra-smoker##2
16. the fan of folk is between the person driving the helicopter and the owner of the mouse##2
17. the person who likes turquise is on the far left or far right##3
