4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, old-henry, oliveros, alhambra
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, ice-hockey, tennis
 1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
 2. the fan of rock is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
