 8. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
12. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
15. the person who likes black is between the old-henry-smoker and the person drinking fanta##2
16. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4
